Uses of Package
com.mhealthatlas.taxonomy.model

Packages that use com.mhealthatlas.taxonomy.model 
Package Description
com.mhealthatlas.taxonomy.command
com.mhealthatlas.taxonomy.command is a group of services which only mutate data but have not advanced query functionalities.
com.mhealthatlas.taxonomy.controller
com.mhealthatlas.taxonomy.controller is a group of REST API controllers in the taxonomy service.
Each class ending with the QueryController prefix provides GET API endpoints for quering information.
Each class ending with the CommandController prefix provides POST and DELETE API endpoints for mutating the information state.
com.mhealthatlas.taxonomy.converter
com.mhealthatlas.taxonomy.converter contains converter to convert entity classes to dto classes.
com.mhealthatlas.taxonomy.dto
com.mhealthatlas.taxonomy.dto contains all data transfer object definitions.
com.mhealthatlas.taxonomy.model
com.mhealthatlas.taxonomy.model contains all entities from the taxonomy service database and the enum declarations.
com.mhealthatlas.taxonomy.query
com.mhealthatlas.taxonomy.query is a group of services which only queries data but does not mutate them.
com.mhealthatlas.taxonomy.repository
com.mhealthatlas.taxonomy.repository contains all repository interfaces of the taxonomy service.
